txt.en: 'Please do not send me to find out!'
'It is not your place to fight those who serve the Black Word!'
'Why don't they come back after I send them down to find treasure?!'
'I never thought I'd leave this place alive...'
'They keep asking about a Ring! I don't know anything about that!'
'I tell them I don't know about the Ring! What more do they want from me?!'
'Even the Uruks treated us better than this lot!'
